Risk Management & Asset Protection


Mitigating risk is an important part of a wealth management strategy. We offer a full array of risk management services, which include advice on property and casualty insurance, and asset protection structures.
Limiting the exposure of personal assets from risks associated with your professional or business interests is vital to safeguarding against litigation. These strategies can be as simple as obtaining an appropriate amount of liability insurance, or as complex as creating trusts that make it more difficult for a creditor to discover and seize your assets. Regardless of the strategy, you can take comfort in knowing that Capstone will go the distance to protect the assets you have worked hard to build, and will recommend strategies that are in the best interest of you and your family. Services offered include:

Coverage analysis
Liability exposure management
Facilitation and recommendation of property and casualty coverage
Recommendations for personal insurance, including life, health, long-term care and disability


 





