Brian Niksa (CRD# 6314089) is an Investment Advisor Representative working at Capstone Financial Advisors Inc. in Downers Grove, IL since 2009. Brian is a Certified Financial Planner (CFP®) providing comprehensive financial, tax and estate planning services to high net worth professionals, families and business owners. He focuses on providing unbiased, pro-active, comprehensive financial planning and has experience working with a variety of clients including physicians, corporate executives, business owners and retirees. In addition to financial planning, Brian has also worked in the financial valuation industry and has experience consulting for local Chicago-area businesses and real estate developers
Specialties:  Corporate Long Term Incentive Planning, Income Tax Planning, Divorce and Retirement Matters, Estates and Trusts.





